reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 13, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great case for machine embroidery enthusiasts
reviews.reviewText: I loved the size, that it zippered. Fits perfectly in my designated drawer with my other embroidery tools. The labels are too big for the sticks, and not permanent enough for the outside of each slot, but for the price of the case, which was very reasonable, I’ll make do :-) great service, and delivery

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 18, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Organizes USB Flash Drives Easily!
reviews.reviewText: Rather than take a chance on losing the flash drives that I have, I ordered this case. The flash drives fit snugly into each slot, and the accompanying labels allow for easy identification of each drive. The case is soft and compact, and keeps the drives safe and organized. Highly recommend.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 1, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Just the Thing for Flash Drives
reviews.reviewText: If you have a lot of flash drives, this is just the thing you need. I found that the small stick-on labels provided with the case were not big enough for me. In fact, I used Avery Return Address labels and typed the contents of each flash on the labels and stuck them on the case. They are a trifle too wide for the job and they don't stick all that well, but some clear scotch tape helps a lot. The case is well-made and should hold up fine.
